sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>Argo v2 or Tekton v1
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Pod as Pipeline Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>9000/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: User Submits Pipeline via Dashboard

    User->>Dashboard: Create pipeline
    Dashboard->>Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>Bearer Token (OAuth)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward request
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate token
    OAuth->>API: Forward (HTTP/8888)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>3306/TCP
    DB-->>API: Confirmation
    API->>WFC: Create workflow<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Service Account
    WFC-->>API: Workflow created
    API-->>OAuth: Success response
    OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Dashboard: Pipeline created
    Dashboard-->>User: Confirmation

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution & Artifact Storage

    WFC->>K8s: Create pipeline pod<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>SA Token
    K8s-->>Pod: Pod scheduled
    Pod->>API: Report status<br/>8887/TCP gRPC<br/>SA Token
    Pod->>S3: Store artifacts<br/>9000/443 HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Access Key
    S3-->>Pod: Artifacts stored
    Pod->>API: Update execution status<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    PA->>API: Query workflow status<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>SA Token
    API-->>PA: Workflow status
    PA->>DB: Update run metadata<br/>3306/TCP
    DB-->>PA: Updated

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: ML Metadata Tracking

    Pod->>API: Log metadata<br/>8887/TCP gRPC<br/>SA Token
    API->>MLMD: Store lineage<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    MLMD->>DB: Persist metadata<br/>3306/TCP
    DB-->>MLMD: Stored
    MLMD-->>API: Confirmation
    API-->>Pod: Acknowledged

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 4: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    ScheduledWF->>K8s: Check cron schedule<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>SA Token
    K8s-->>ScheduledWF: Time to execute
    ScheduledWF->>API: Create pipeline run<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>SA Token
    API->>WFC: Trigger workflow<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Service Account
    WFC->>K8s: Create pipeline pod<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8s-->>Pod: Pod scheduled
